N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 65.70 - Restrictions on Commissioner of Labor's participation

State Regulations

In any proceeding noticed pursuant to these rules, the

Commissioner of Labor shall not participate in or advise with respect to any
decision of the Board. Notes
